casebody.data:
Friday, November 15, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-2501. Nozik v. Sanson.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 69948 and 70198. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellants’ motion for stay of execution of court of appeals’ judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.
